===Etymology===
From {{m|fr|rêver||to dream}}, from {{etyl|frm|fr}} {{m|frm|resver||to wander, be lost in vague thoughts, guess inaccurately}}, from {{etyl|fro|fr}} {{m|fro|resver||to consider, reflect, be delirious}}, probably from {{etyl|frk|fr}} *{{m|frk||rēswan, *rāswan|to consider, conjecture, guess}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|fr}} {{m|gem-pro|*rēswaną||to think, reckon, calculate}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|fr}} {{m|ine-pro|*rei-||to reason, count}}. Cognate with {{etyl|ang|-}} {{m|ang|sc=Latinx|rǣswan||to think, consider, suspect, conjecture}}. Related to {{etyl|got|-}} {{m|got|𐍂𐌰𐌸𐌾𐍉||account, number, explanation}}, {{etyl|goh|-}} {{m|goh|rīm||number}}. More at {{l|en|rhyme}}.

